import React from "react";
import { Card, CardHeader, CardBody,Text,Box,Stack,StackDivider,Heading } from "@chakra-ui/react";
function Solutions(){
    return (
      <Card width="400px" mt={15} bg="transparent" bord>
        <CardHeader mb={-5}>
          <Heading size="md">Solutions</Heading>
        </CardHeader>
        <CardBody>
          <Stack divider={<StackDivider />} spacing="1">
            <Box>
              <Text fontSize="sm">Improved Performance</Text>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Text fontSize="sm">Scalability</Text>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Text fontSize="sm">
                Optimized Network Bandwidth Usage in Cloud
              </Text>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Text fontSize="sm">Better resource utilization</Text>
            </Box>
          </Stack>
        </CardBody>
      </Card>
    );
}
export default Solutions;
